{"tid":1420401,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關於記者會嘅建議","createTime":"2019-08-06T04:29:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T04:31:31.000Z","uid":58200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e5b6ad47fffb49659acf87d0275965e41e83266f","tid":1420401,"uid":58200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:29:17.000Z","msg":"集中討論兩個最致命問題<br />\n<br />\n1. 代表性<br />\n由於唔可以做大台, 一定唔可以代表抗爭者承諾啲乜嘢, 但有方法可以提升代表性, <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最直接係每次記者會後喺連登開一個post, 由所有連登仔評價代唔代表到自己嘅意見, <span style=\"color: red;\">正評/負評 = 信任/不信任票</span><br />\n連登已經算係一個公認有代表性嘅網絡平台, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果多數連登仔正評, 已經足夠反映代表性</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2. 前線武力行為, 不割蓆, 無底線問題<br />\n- 強調每個抗爭者做法唔同, 唔可以代任何抗爭者承諾, 只可以呼籲和平, 唔好傷害到人<br />\n- 強調不割蓆係指要團結, 唔代表係無底線, <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">底線係良知</span></span></strong><br />\n- <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">強調市民同媒體會較容易見到示威者對&quot;物件&quot;嘅損壞但暫時未見有示威者傷害平民, 反而多次保護平民</span></strong><br />\n- 呼籲集中關注警方嘅武力對平民嘅傷害"},{"pid":"e89d2fc24bfa85524832a1e639f18ad12e4dc5d1","tid":1420401,"uid":58200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:30:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a00c812445847d2330b19592e2e8c732a0bb794","tid":1420401,"uid":58200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be77539c643bb5788c851458758705f8d2769c5d","tid":1420401,"uid":280349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:31:31.000Z","msg":"再post: 文宣攻勢開始啦，打左啲野大家幫手spread啊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417298</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}